These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, skateboarding, cycling, rowing
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, grapes, pineapple
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, mystery, horror, sports
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, egyptian, american, australian
 1. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person eating pineapple##1
 3. the brazilian is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the american is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 5. the brazilian is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
 7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 8. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 9. the brazilian is on the far left##1
10. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
11. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| Sport    | cycling   | skateboarding       | rugby | rowing   |
| Food        | banana    | pineapple  | grapes      | apple |
| Movie-Genre         | sports      | mystery | horror         | musical   |
| Nationality   | brazilian | egyptian       | american        | australian   |

