.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-2::.
City: miami, new-york, venice, berlin
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, bolivar, blend, old-henry
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rowing, soccer, tennis
4 different games are played: poker, domino, billiard, mah-jongg
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is the prince-smoker##1
3. the person playing billiard is the person traveling to venice##1
4. the person traveling to miami is between the bolivar-smoker and the person playing poker##2
5. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing domino##1
6. the person who's sport is tennis is the person playing mah-jongg##1
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
8. the person playing poker is on the far left or far right##3
9. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |       3        |      4       |
| City           | new-york | miami | berlin | venice |
| Cigar   | prince  | blend | bolivar         | old-henry      |
| Sport         | soccer      | rowing    | tennis         | ice-hockey   |
| Game     | poker         | domino    | mah-jongg          | billiard         |

