.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, azalea, orchid, sunflower
House: ranch-style, gothic-revival, craftsman, modern
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, october, april, december
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, ice-hockey, volleyball
 1. the craftsman house is the person who growsorchid##1
 2. the ranch-style house is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the modern house##1
 6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
 7. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the gothic-revival house##2
 9. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
10. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Flower          | azalea | sunflower  | zinnia | orchid      |
| House   | ranch-style       | modern    | gothic-revival      | craftsman      |
| Birthday           | december     | may     | october         | april   |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | cricket | cycling     | volleyball |

