7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
8. the videographer is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who likes brown##2
9. the librarian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4       |
