4 different games are played: poker, whist, mah-jongg, monopoly
 1. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
 2. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 4. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
 8. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
 9. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person playing whist##1
10. the person who likes black is between the person driving the skateboard and the person who likes lilac##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
| Transport      | quad-bike | skateboard | helicopter     | taxi       |
| Food          | carrot   | zucchini    | pineapple | kiwi       |
| Color   | mauve     | ivory       | black    | lilac     |
