 2. the person who's sport is cricket is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 3. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 9. the person eating pomegranate is the person who likes green##1
10. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3       |     4     |
| Hobby         | chess      | video-games | sudoku       | drawing   |
| Sport   | weightlifting     | badminton | skiing | cricket |
| Color   | turquise    | fuchsia     | purple        | green       |
| Food     | grapes | pepper   | watermelon   | pomegranate       |

