.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, iris, daffodil, marigold
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, 7up, cola
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, mystery, satire
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, brazilian, spanish, dutch
 1. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
 2. the brazilian is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 3. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is between the spanish and the brazilian##2
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
 6. the person watching adventure movies is between the person drinking sprite and the indonesian##2
 7. the person watching mystery movies is the person drinking cola##1
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the person who growsdaffodil is the person drinking sprite##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Flower          | iris | marigold   | daffodil   | poppy |
| Beverage           | juice   | 7up     | sprite   | cola |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | adventure    | satire   | mystery   |
| Nationality         | indonesian    | brazilian | dutch | spanish    |

 